CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.F_CTS_O_Dispatch (
	[DispatchID] bigint,
	[DispatchSite] nvarchar(4000),
	[DispatchDate] date,
	[dispatch.vehicletype] int,
	[TotalTripTimeMin] numeric(10,2),
	[TotalTripTimeMHrs] numeric(10,2),
	[PlanTotalTripTimeMin] numeric(10,2),
	[PlanTotalTripTimeHrs] numeric(10,2),
	[TotalTripKms] numeric(10,2),
	[OdoKms] numeric(10,2),
	[PlanTotalTripKms] numeric(10,2),
	[VehicleType] int,
	[DropCnt] bigint,
	[WaybillCnt] bigint,
	[DropDistanceAvg] numeric(10,2),
	[DropDurationAvgMin] numeric(10,2),
	[DropDurationAvgHrs] numeric(10,2)
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'DataLake/Structured/Facts/F_CTS_O_Dispatch.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.F_CTS_O_Dispatch
GO
